The paper discusses the development of massively parallel algorithms for programmable logic devices (PLDs), which involves hardware synthesis methodologies and reconfigurable computing. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Architecture (cs.AR), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Software Engineering (cs.SE).
